data.description: Explore this cozy two-story home boasting 3 bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms. Step into a residence that provides ample space to suit your lifestyle. The recently updated kitchen showcases a stylish central island with a spacious pantry. Ascend to the second floor, revealing three bedrooms and a full bathroom. Notable upgrades include the furnace, water heater, and windows. Experience the charm of recently added kitchen floors and a freshly painted interior. The fenced-in yard offers privacy for outdoor enjoyment, while the full basement provides a customizable space. Indoors, the elevated ceilings create an airy atmosphere, complemented by ceiling fans that enhance overall comfort. Don't let the opportunity pass to claim this home as your very own!
